Some tips and infomation:

1) If you press F during the game the screen will follow the selected unit.

2) To delete a whole bunch of units, in the editor, just select them with

   the right mouse button and press delete.

3) To delete a building or a "lidium pool", then select a building icon or

   the "lidium pool" icon and press delete.

4) Use the trigger editor to make much more advanced missions.

5) Chain two or more Missions together for long campaigns using the

   EkstraEditor.

6) You can also change the units/buildings properties using the

   EkstraEditor.

7) Use the trigger system to make advanced missions.

8) load the CustomMission in the savedmissions/ dir into the EkstraEditor to

   see how the trigger system works.

9) Add passwords to your missions in the EkstraEditor.

                            New:

10) Move units by right clicking in the game map.

11) Create groups of units with F1-F10 buttons, and call them with 1-0
    buttons.
